//
//  Cities:  GeoNames (CC BY 4.0, https://www.geonames.org/), population >= 50000.
//           City districts (Hamburg-Mitte, Bucharest "Sector 3", ...) are removed:
//           a place lying within 12 km of a city at least 3x larger is treated as
//           a district of it. Names are transliterated to ASCII, because the GFX
//           font has no glyphs for diacritics.
//
//  Coordinates are stored as uint16 fixed point to halve the flash cost:
//      degrees = ORIGIN + value * EU_COORD_SCALE
